; Tests for the clear_commodity() function
; Removes the commodity from an amount, returning just the numeric quantity

2012-01-01 Test clear_commodity function
    Assets:Test                       $100.00
    Equity:Opening

; Positive test: remove commodity from dollar amount
test eval 'clear_commodity($100)'
100
end test

; Positive test: remove commodity from EUR amount
test eval 'clear_commodity(50 EUR)'
